reviewText: Enlightens people to the fact it is more than than a history of the Jews and introduction of Christ, but it also has prophecy encoded within the Hebrew language that concerns the future events that has taken place...such as 911, the holocaust, and other events....Everyone should at least watch this DVD and make up their own minds.  It definitely proves that God is God, and Jesus (also God) is His Son sent to earth to die for our sins.
